# YogaBuddy Model Training Visualizations

Here is a summary of the training run metrics for the 82-class model, depicting model convergence over epochs, and classification performance across classes.

## Training & Validation Curves

The following plots show categorical cross-entropy loss diminishing over time, paired with robust accuracy on both the training and validation splits.

![Training Curves](/Users/aniruddhmodi/.gemini/antigravity/brain/4acd978f-6be7-4fc5-8403-b56e60562527/artifacts/training_curves.png)

## Confusion Matrix

The normalized confusion matrix illustrates the density of true positives along the diagonal. A few classes exhibit minor cross-confusion (expected given the nuanced, subtle differences among total 82 Yoga poses).

![Confusion Matrix](/Users/aniruddhmodi/.gemini/antigravity/brain/4acd978f-6be7-4fc5-8403-b56e60562527/artifacts/confusion_matrix.png)
